The paper deals with communication complexity and graph labeling, which are both topics in theoretical computer science. Specifically, the paper introduces a new communication model and applies it to graph labeling problems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CC (Computational Complexity), followed by cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
